edit the trusted hostes 


sudo nextcloud.occ config:system:set trusted_domains 1 --value=example.com



add talk to your next cloud

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RPireLVSPAo
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------


    Install Nextcloud

sudo snap install nextcloud

    Make admin account

sudo nextcloud.manual-install ADMINUSER PASSWORD

    Add Trusted Domains

sudo nextcloud.occ config:system:set trusted_domains 1 --value=YOUR.DOMAIN.HERE

    Open firewall ports in /etc/iptables/rules.v4 add two lines below:

iptables -I INPUT -p tcp -m tcp --dport 443 -j ACCEPT
iptables -I INPUT -p tcp -m tcp --dport 80 -j ACCEPT

    Reload iptables running config 

iptables-restore 'ï¼œ' /etc/iptables/rules.v4

    Set SSL

sudo nextcloud.enable-https lets-encrypt

    To renew SSL

sudo snap refresh
